[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":342},["Reactive",2],{"new-blog-2024":3,"content-query-fa68aGlRqd":205},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":7,"_locale":8,"title":9,"description":10,"date":11,"tags":12,"slug":15,"readingTime":16,"body":21,"_type":200,"_id":201,"_source":202,"_file":203,"_extension":204},"/articles/new-blog-2024","articles",true,false,"","New Blog!","New stack, who dis?","2024-02-27T00:00:00.000Z",[13,14],"personal","nuxt","new-blog-2024",{"text":17,"minutes":18,"time":19,"words":20},"3 min read",2.73,163800,546,{"type":22,"children":23,"toc":193},"root",[24,32,51,58,74,79,85,90,95,100,105,110,115,124,165,177,183,188],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":27,"children":28},"element","p",{},[29],{"type":30,"value":31},"text","After not touching my blog for a couple years, I finally decided on a stack and began to rebuild it. I wanted to outline my journey and tools that got me here.",{"type":25,"tag":33,"props":34,"children":35},"blockquote",{},[36,41],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":37,"children":38},{},[39],{"type":30,"value":40},"Programmers will rewrite their entire blog 10 times before writing a single post.",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":43,"children":44},"ul",{},[45],{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":47,"children":48},"li",{},[49],{"type":30,"value":50},"Some twitter post I saw once",{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":53,"children":55},"h2",{"id":54},"gatsby",[56],{"type":30,"value":57},"Gatsby",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":59,"children":60},{},[61,63,72],{"type":30,"value":62},"In the summer of 2020, I taught myself React and Gatsby by building my blog. This became a great introduction to static site generators. After being a full stack php developer for 3 years, the Dev Experience of Gatsby was a breath of fresh air. I followed a few tutorials from ",{"type":25,"tag":64,"props":65,"children":69},"a",{"href":66,"rel":67},"https://joshwcomeau.com",[68],"nofollow",[70],{"type":30,"value":71},"Josh Comeau",{"type":30,"value":73}," and I had my blog deployed by the end of the week. It was a fun time despite the world being on fire.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":75,"children":76},{},[77],{"type":30,"value":78},"Unfortunately, I didn't keep up with the blog. I didn't use React professionally or in any side projects, so solving problems in Gatsby took longer than I wanted. It became harder and harder to fill my brain with programming knowledge that was only useful for one thing. Not to mention Gatsby was starting to become very slow when building my site and would randomly break because some package updated. All of that plus life changes, I didn't have the energy to keep posting or maintaining the blog.",{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":80,"children":82},{"id":81},"eleventy",[83],{"type":30,"value":84},"Eleventy",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":86,"children":87},{},[88],{"type":30,"value":89},"After a year of not doing much with my personal site, I decided I wanted to write it in a simpler stack, something I was more familiar with. Nothing is more simple than vanilla js.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":91,"children":92},{},[93],{"type":30,"value":94},"Around this time, I kept hearing about Eleventy on podcasts. I decided to give it a look and was impressed by how simple it was. Everything is just JS, no magic. That turned out however to be a bad thing. One thing Gatsby had is a swarm of plugins for every problem you could think of. 11ty had a number of plugins too, but you would have to really dig into the config and code if you wanted to replicate a similar dev experience as Gatsby.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":96,"children":97},{},[98],{"type":30,"value":99},"I never ended up finishing the blog in 11ty. That doesn't mean there is anything wrong with 11ty, its a great framework for certain use cases. For me, I wanted something that is hackable but also simple when I just want to write a post. 11ty just required too much work to get it to where I wanted it to be.",{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":101,"children":102},{"id":14},[103],{"type":30,"value":104},"Nuxt",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":106,"children":107},{},[108],{"type":30,"value":109},"Queue to 2024, you are most likely reading this post on a site built with Nuxt. After doing a bit of research, I found Nuxt which is similar to NextJS but written for Vue. Nuxt is pretty cool, its got a lot of Dev Ex features like Gatsby does but its all in Vue. In about a day and a half, I had my blog set up with all of the posts from my old site.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":111,"children":112},{},[113],{"type":30,"value":114},"Vue has been my goto framework professionally for the last 5 years. So learning Nuxt is not too difficult.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":116,"children":117},{},[118],{"type":25,"tag":119,"props":120,"children":121},"strong",{},[122],{"type":30,"value":123},"My current stack is:",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":125,"children":126},{},[127,150,155,160],{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":128,"children":129},{},[130,132],{"type":30,"value":131},"Nuxt 3\n",{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":133,"children":134},{},[135,140,145],{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":136,"children":137},{},[138],{"type":30,"value":139},"Nuxt Content",{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":141,"children":142},{},[143],{"type":30,"value":144},"Nuxt Image",{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":146,"children":147},{},[148],{"type":30,"value":149},"Nuxt SEO",{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":151,"children":152},{},[153],{"type":30,"value":154},"TailwindCSS",{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":156,"children":157},{},[158],{"type":30,"value":159},"Coolify for hosting",{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":161,"children":162},{},[163],{"type":30,"value":164},"Markdown",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":166,"children":167},{},[168,170],{"type":30,"value":169},"Also, I decided to fully open source my blog. You can find the code on ",{"type":25,"tag":64,"props":171,"children":174},{"href":172,"rel":173},"https://github.com/GeorgeNance/blog24",[68],[175],{"type":30,"value":176},"Github",{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":178,"children":180},{"id":179},"conclusion",[181],{"type":30,"value":182},"Conclusion",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":184,"children":185},{},[186],{"type":30,"value":187},"Nothing says \"I want to write a blog post\" like rewriting your entire blog. I am happy with the stack I have chosen. I am excited to write more posts and share my knowledge with the world.",{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":189,"children":190},{},[191],{"type":30,"value":192},"Expect more posts soon! 📓",{"title":8,"searchDepth":194,"depth":194,"links":195},2,[196,197,198,199],{"id":54,"depth":194,"text":57},{"id":81,"depth":194,"text":84},{"id":14,"depth":194,"text":104},{"id":179,"depth":194,"text":182},"markdown","content:articles:new-blog-2024.md","content","articles/new-blog-2024.md","md",{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":7,"_locale":8,"title":9,"description":10,"date":11,"tags":206,"slug":15,"readingTime":207,"body":208,"_type":200,"_id":201,"_source":202,"_file":203,"_extension":204},[13,14],{"text":17,"minutes":18,"time":19,"words":20},{"type":22,"children":209,"toc":336},[210,214,228,232,242,246,250,254,258,262,266,270,274,281,315,324,328,332],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":211,"children":212},{},[213],{"type":30,"value":31},{"type":25,"tag":33,"props":215,"children":216},{},[217,221],{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":218,"children":219},{},[220],{"type":30,"value":40},{"type":25,"tag":42,"props":222,"children":223},{},[224],{"type":25,"tag":46,"props":225,"children":226},{},[227],{"type":30,"value":50},{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":229,"children":230},{"id":54},[231],{"type":30,"value":57},{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":233,"children":234},{},[235,236,241],{"type":30,"value":62},{"type":25,"tag":64,"props":237,"children":239},{"href":66,"rel":238},[68],[240],{"type":30,"value":71},{"type":30,"value":73},{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245],{"type":30,"value":78},{"type":25,"tag":52,"props":247,"children":248},{"id":81},[249],{"type":30,"value":84},{"type":25,"tag":26,"props":251,"children":252},{},[253],{"type":30,"value":89},{"type":25,